title: US in danger of missing Olympic men's soccer again
text:
> Sports US in danger of missing Olympic men's soccer again United States forward Jerome Kiesewetter, left, falls after being pushed by Honduras defender Marcelo Pereira, right, during a tussle between teams in the second half of a CONCACAF men's Olympics semifinal qualifying soccer match, Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015, in Sandy, Utah. Honduras won 2-0. (AP Photo/Rick Bowmer) Search Help
